node.text:
Midsummer solstice is upon us, marking the turning of the sun, and the longest day of 2020 in the northern hemisphere ☀️
Together with @Midgardsblot, @kalandramusic are excited to invite you to their first-ever live stream from the hall of Midgard Saturday 20th at 22:30 CET.
And @kalandramusic just told me they will play their cover song that I've used in this video ⚔️ do you recognize it??
Link in bio to the event!!
.
The clips in this video are from various adventures with @mariestokka and @fenris_the_vikingdog

node.text:
Did you hear about the new products from @thebeardstruggle ?👑
We now have a beard growth serum that's supposed to help with patchy beard and promote growth 🔥
.
🍻Check it out, LINK IN BIO!!🍻
🤑20% discount with code PILOT
.
I have some patchy spots in my beard, so have just started to use this myself in combination with the Derma Roller.
I do it about 2-3 timer per week, so excited to check out the results in a couple of months! 🙏
.
Video by @marius.mohmedia
